Class Description
AccessPeriod

Course  
CourseClashingException
Exception thrown when the total weightage component does not tally up correctly.
CourseCodeNotFoundException
Exception when the user inputs an invalid course index

Exception when the user inputs an invalid course index
EmailManager
EmailManager is the class containing the logic to perform email sending
ExistingCourseException
Exception thrown when user registers the same course index.
IllegalAUWeightageException
Exception thrown when the total AU weightage component exceeds 21 AUs.
IllegalCourseChangeException
Exception thrown when the course index the user is trying to change to is from a different course code.
IllegalTimeFormatException
Exception thrown when the time formatting is not according to the specified format.
IllegalTimePeriodException
Exception thrown when the time period is not the user has included is not possible.
IllegalVacancyException
Exception when the target vacancy is less than the previous vacancy size for the course index.
LoginController
Logincontroller contains the logic to validate the Users during the login processes
LoginUI
User Interface Boundary Class for Users to Login
PasswordManager
PasswordManager class handles all password related jobs, such as salt hashing passwords using the PBKDF2-HMAC-SHA1 hashing algorithm to secure passwords, and verifying passwords with the salt hashed passwords.
Staff
Staff represents a staff in the school.
StaffController
StaffController contains the logic to realise use case of the options given to the admin in the StaffUI.
StaffUI
Boundary Class that limits the user to carry out only Staff functions Implements the UserUI interface
Student
Student represents a student in the school.
StudentController
StudentController contains the logic to realise use case of the options given to the student in the StudentUI.
StudentUI
Boundary Class that limits the user to carry out only Student functions A subclass of the UserUI class
Ultility
Utility is the class containing oft-used utility methods for input validation
User
User represents a user in the database.
UserNotFoundException
Exception when there is no user found in the database.
UserUI
Interface to fulfill Dependency Injection Principle
